    public class JndiMessage

    SolReserved - Represents a JNDI request or response message. Responses are read-only and may not be modified.

      • setPayload

        public void setPayload(byte[] payloadBytes)
        Set the message payload for a JNDI request.

        If this is a JNDI response message, the payload is read-only and calling this method results in an IllegalAccessError.

        Parameters:
        payloadBytes - Payload to set on the request. It is copied into the message.
